FT  20 OCT 94 / UK Company News: Glenchewton deficit reduced
Glenchewton reduced pre-tax losses for the six months to June 30 from Pounds
463,000 to Pounds 293,000 having ended 1993 with a pre-tax profit of Pounds
606,000.
Turnover at the toys and housewares importer was down slightly at Pounds 8m
(Pounds 8.2m).
There were restructuring expenses of Pounds 21,000, while last year's
figures took into account the recovery of Pounds 35,000 in property
litigation costs.
